// Customer Module API Tests

### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050/api/customers
// @token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get all customers
GET {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Search customers
GET {{baseUrl}}?search=tech
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Create a new customer (Directly)
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "type": "Company",
  "name": "Acme Corp",
  "contactPerson": "John Smith",
  "email": "john@acme.com",
  "phone": "+1 234 567 8900",
  "city": "New York",
  "status": "Active"
}

###

### 4. Convert Lead to Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/convert-lead
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "leadId": "UUID_OF_CONVERTED_LEAD"
}

###

### 5. Get customer by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/CUSTOMER_UUID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Update customer
PUT {{baseUrl}}/CUSTOMER_UUID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "notes": "Updated notes via API",
  "status": "Inactive"
}

###

### 7. Delete customer
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/CUSTOMER_UUID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
